room_title: Escape room "Casino Heist" by Which Way Out Knoxville in Knoxville
room_description: $500,000 is missing from the Stardust Casino. According to surveillance cameras, suspected thief William John Brennan left the Stardust empty-handed at 1:30 PM and hasn’t been seen since – leading many to believe the loot is still somewhere inside. The impatient casino manager has given your team of crack investigators has just 60 minutes to find the lost money and make it out of the casino before another team gets their shot at finding the money – and claiming the reward.
